com.soa.delegate.config

Class DynamicProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soa.delegate.config.DynamicProperties
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DelegateConfiguration

    public class DynamicProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Provide a mechanism that will allow consumer applications to dynamically specify Client Delegate configuration properties at run-time. This is needed to, for instance, pass in user credentials programmatically or to store and present properties using some application-specific mechanism like a database.
    Since:
    6.0
